c: 2
v: 246
t: Vos noted dux Israel Moses They dictus to their prophet vos appoint rex lead nos nos fight causa DEUS. He dictus Est it tuus intention fighting decretum vos vos non fight They dictus should nos non fight causa DEUS when nos deprived de noster domus noster infans? Autem when fighting decretum them they turned ut few DEUS est aware de transgressors